Start
/ Migrating a non-migratable channel (console-backed Stream) returns NotMigratable.
/ output is a Channel.Stream backed by Console.OpenStandardOutput at boot — process-bound.
- set %targetIdentity% = 'peer'
- migrate channel "output" to %targetIdentity%, on error set %notMigratable% = true
- assert %notMigratable% is true
